  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://img.wdjimg.com/mms/icon/v1/b/7a/1b7ac6f8826971800db4c448dc1637ab_256_256.png\" /></p>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<p style=\"line-height: 25px;\">\n\t\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p785448\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n\t<p style=\"line-height: 25px;\">\n\t\tToday young men return to the Spanish countryside as <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/austerity\" target=\"_blank\">austerity</a> bites in the big cities. Droughts, the threat in the American state of Nebraska - there farmers say they're losing the battle against the elements. We walk through the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/poppy\" target=\"_blank\">poppy</a> fields of Gallipoli, 97 years after a battle, in which 130,000 lives were lost, and the locals are on holiday. The streets are quiet, the air is <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/pure\" target=\"_blank\">pure</a>. August in Paris, it's like a month of Sundays.</p>\n\t<p style=\"line-height: 25px;\">\n\t\tThere are clouds gathering over the Spanish government this weekend. It's reported to be close to seeking a multi-billion-euro bailout from the EU and the European Central Bank. That'll mean further deep <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/austerity\" target=\"_blank\">austerity</a> measures, which in turn could lead to protests on the streets, even a general strike. Trades Union representatives met King Juan Carlos earlier this week. They told him they were opposed to the new rescue package because it would increase the hardship for Spaniards already suffering from two years of <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/harsh\" target=\"_blank\">harsh</a> austerity measures.</p>\n\t<p style=\"line-height: 25px;\">\n\t\tChris Stewart who lives and farms in the south of the country says the economic crisis is having some unexpected consequences in rural communities.</p>\n\t<p style=\"line-height: 25px;\">\n\t\t&quot;No hay mal que por bien no venga&quot; is what the Spanish say when they want to point out that every cloud has a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/silver\" target=\"_blank\">silver</a> lining. 20 years ago, Peck Sanchez and I used to talk about a utopia, in which all the abandoned land in the Alpujarra would be beautifully farmed. We dreamed that young people, tired of the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/blandishment\" target=\"_blank\">blandishments</a> of urban life, would return to the land, burning with agricultural idealism and would recreate the garden of Eden that we believed existed here 500 years ago when the Moors ran the show.&nbsp;</p>\n\t<p style=\"line-height: 25px;\">\n\t\t<span>声明：音视频均来自互联网链接，仅供学习使用。本网站自身不存储、控制、修改被链接的内容。&ldquo;沪江</span><a>英语</a><span>&rdquo;高度重视知识产权保护。当如发现本网站发布的信息包含有侵犯其著作权的链接内容时，请联系我们，我们将依法采取措施移除相关内容或屏蔽相关链接。&gt;&gt;<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/course/52569?source=16553\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0,90,148);\" target=\"_blank\">零基础直达流利生活口语班</a>&lt;&lt;</span></p>\n</div>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p785448/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p785448\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p793363/\">近万人参加的反脱欧游行：这些标语看笑了</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p790655/\">周迅英文全靠嫁人？英语倍溜的老公何方神圣</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p793312/\">马特达蒙麻省理工2016毕业演讲 附语言点</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p793530/\">脱欧后 要和英国洽谈合作的国家已排起了长队</a